## ðŸ‘¤ Table: `gold.dim_customers`

| Column Name       | Data Type      | Description                       | Purpose                     |
|-------------------|----------------|-----------------------------------|-----------------------------|
| customer_key      | bigint         | Surrogate key for customer        | Primary Key                 |
| customer_id       | int            | Natural/business key              | External system reference   |
| customer_number   | nvarchar(50)   | Internal customer number          | Operational tracking        |
| first_name        | nvarchar(50)   | Customerâ€™s first name             | Personalization             |
| last_name         | nvarchar(50)   | Customerâ€™s last name              | Personalization             |
| country           | nvarchar(50)   | Country of residence              | Geo segmentation            |
| marital_status    | nvarchar(50)   | Marital status                    | Demographic analysis        |
| gender            | nvarchar(50)   | Gender                            | Demographic analysis        |
| birthdate         | date           | Date of birth                     | Age-based segmentation      |
| create_date       | date           | Date customer was added to system| Customer lifecycle analysis |

