## ðŸ“¦ Table: `gold.dim_products`

| Column Name     | Data Type      | Description                          | Purpose                  |
|-----------------|----------------|--------------------------------------|--------------------------|
| product_key     | bigint         | Surrogate key for product            | Primary Key              |
| product_id      | int            | Natural/business key                 | External system reference|
| product_number  | nvarchar(50)   | Internal product code                | SKU tracking             |
| product_name    | nvarchar(50)   | Name of the product                  | Display & reporting      |
| category_id     | nvarchar(50)   | ID of the product category           | Hierarchical grouping    |
| category        | nvarchar(50)   | Name of the category                 | Category-level analysis  |
| subcategory_id  | nvarchar(50)   | ID of the subcategory                | Granular grouping        |
| subcategory     | nvarchar(50)   | Name of the subcategory              | Granular grouping        |
| cost            | int            | Cost to produce or acquire product   | Margin analysis          |
| product_line    | nvarchar(50)   | Product line or brand                | Strategic grouping       |
| start_date      | date           | Launch date of the product           | Product lifecycle analysis|

---

## ðŸ“… Table: `gold.dim_time` *(Assumed Standard Time Dimension)*

| Column Name  | Data Type      | Description           | Purpose                  |
|--------------|----------------|-----------------------|--------------------------|
| date_key     | int            | Surrogate key for date| Primary Key              |
| date         | date           | Calendar date         | Join with fact table     |
| year         | int            | Year component        | Time aggregation         |
| quarter      | nvarchar(10)   | Quarter (e.g., Q1)    | Seasonal trends          |
| month        | nvarchar(20)   | Month name            | Monthly reporting        |
| day          | int            | Day of month          | Daily granularity        |
| weekday      | nvarchar(20)   | Day of week           | Weekday/weekend analysis |
| is_holiday   | bit            | Flag for public holidays | Holiday impact analysis|

